Class Participant

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.psychic_engine.cmput301w17t10.feelsappman.Controllers.ModelFrame
      • com.psychic_engine.cmput301w17t10.feelsappman.Models.Participant

  • public class Participant
extends ModelFrame
    Participant model to describe the attributes of the participant. Each participant upon signup will hold their own personal arrays of mood events, followers, following, and pending requests. Currently the last three are out of service until later development.
    See Also:
    LoginActivity
